text: :Moez Ben Abdelkader Fezzani may refer to: * Moez Ben Abdelkader Fezzani is an alternate name for Adel Ben Mabrouk, an individual formerly held in Guantanamo * Moez Bin Abdul Qadir Fezzani (Bagram detainee), is an individual formerly held in Bagram, who has been confused with the similarly named individual held in Guantanamo
title: Moez Ben Abdelkader Fezzani
